            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Soli <lb n="2"/>Invict<lb break="no" n="3"/>o <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Iu<lb break="no" n="4"/>nianus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aefecti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberfläche des Inschriftfeldes teilweise stark verwittert. Z. 3/4: AVR und NINIANV in Ligatur. Z. 5: sc. praefecti legionis. Z. 6 befindet sich auf der crepido. (B): CIL 03, 04301; CIMRM; RIU; Schallmyer - Eibl - Ott - Preuß - Wittkopf: Lesung abweichend / unvollständig.</p>
            </div>
